org.livingdoc.api.documents

Annotation Type Group


  • @Testable
 @Target
 @Retention
public Group

    A Group contains a number of annotationclass ExecutableDocument, which are executed together. The execution of different Groups is guaranteed to happen in sequence. A Group can also define annotationclass Before and annotationclass After hooks, which are run before or after all documents.

    See Also:
    annotationclass ExecutableDocument, annotationclass Before, annotationclass After, annotationclass ExecutableDocument, annotationclass Before, annotationclass After
